{"tid":2004451,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"NASA 力助 Tom Cruise 上國際太空站拍攝電影","createTime":"2020-05-06T12:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T12:54:30.000Z","uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5bafedf3bde0dd2e4abf949d1dc665b02abc388a","tid":2004451,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T12:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdimse%2F5845cadfecd996e0372f%2Ff7280d18cd8aab2630ec1ee3791c07fd13ecb870%2FdGh1bWJuYWlsPTY0MCUyQyZxdWFsaXR5PTgwJmltYWdlX3VyaT1odHRwcyUzQSUyRiUyRnMueWltZy5jb20lMkZvcyUyRmNyZWF0ci11cGxvYWRlZC1pbWFnZXMlMkYyMDIwLTA1JTJGZTg1YzY3NDAtOGYxMC0xMWVhLWFiZmEtMWJmMmJlMDc5OTczJmNsaWVudD1hbXAtYmxvZ3NpZGUtdjImc2lnbmF0dXJlPTRiMjZiOWMwMWRlNTQ0M2FjMWZhM2Q5ZDZlMThjOTcwNDQzYTUyYzA%3D&h=77c0b3c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNASA 在尋求商業機遇這件事上最近又有了新的進展。局長 Jim Bridenstine 日前在接受 Deadline 採訪時證實，Tom Cruise 將在其幫助下於國際太空站內拍攝一部新的電影。如果一切順利的話，那這部作品應該會成為首部在真實太空中取景的劇情影片（不是那些在低重力飛機裡拍出來的「普通」片子）。雖然 Bridenstine 沒有深入談及更多細節，但從之前的坊間流言來推測，這部戲應該跟 Cruise 的代表作《不可能的任務》沒有關係。<br />\n<br />\n在該報導中還提到 SpaceX 也會參與其中，不過考慮到 NASA 跟他們之間的密切合作關係，聽到這個名字老實講也不算什麼意外。據稱這部電影目前仍處在非常初步的籌備階段，電影公司都還沒有參與進來，而且也沒有確定上映時間（做為參考，SpaceX 最早也要明年下半年才會開放用 Crew Dragon 送遊客上太空站的服務）。<br />\n<br />\n從合作的角度出發，這部影片可以說是一個非常有望雙贏的計劃。Tom Cruise 近些年非常癡迷於在電影裡挑戰自身的極限，而直接上太空拍攝毫無疑問能滿足他在這方面的渴望。而對 NASA 來說，他們「需要流行媒體來激發新一代的工程師和科學家」。此外為了推進國際空間站的商業化，還有什麼比一部「宣傳片」更有噱頭的呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/chinese-2020-05-06-tom-cruise-movie-in-space.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2Fchinese-2020-05-06-tom-cruise-movie-in-space.html&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=d66736f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/chinese-2020-05-06-tom-cruise-movie-in-space.html</a>"},{"pid":"ea1c801784cf83ada235879d757e3a6a7acd064b","tid":2004451,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T12:40:40.000Z","msg":"玩到上宇宙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031c76b5464426539d1f69c6371c5fdc735a29b4","tid":2004451,"uid":350606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T12:54:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}